esse animal parar de sofrer?

180
00:18:00,979 --> 00:18:03,243
<i>Estou tentando explicar
para eles.</i>

181
00:18:03,348 --> 00:18:05,839
Pelo amor de Deus!

182
00:18:27,606 --> 00:18:29,506
Desculpe. Eu...

